'''''Kibera Kid''''' ni filime ngufi yashyizwe mu gace ka Kibera i [[Nairobi]],  [[Kenya]] . Yanditswe, iyobowe kandi ifatanya na Nathan Collett ku bufatanye n’abaturage ba Kibera. 

Iyi filime y'iminota cumi n'ibiri yagaragayemo abakinnyi ba filimi muri Kibera mubikorwa by'ingenzi. Yakinywe mu birori bya firime ku isi yose harimo iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Berlin kandi yatsindiye [[:en:Student_EMMY|Student EMMY]] ukomoka muriHollywood .  Byanditswe na BBC,  Reuters   hamwe na Al Jazeera Icyongereza .  Muri Mata 2009, hafashwe amashusho yerekana amashusho ya Kibera Kid. Filime ndende yuzuye yibanda ku makimbirane ashingiye ku moko ndetse no kwiyunga. Iyi filime yagize ingaruka nini kuko yatumye hashyirwaho Hot Sun Foundation itoza urubyiruko rwo mucyaro gukora firime zabo. 

== Umugambi ==
Kibera Kid ninkuru ya Otieno, impfubyi yimyaka 12 yo muri Kibera abana nitsinda ryabajura bagomba guhitamo ubuzima bw'agatsiko no gucungurwa. Inkuru ni ibihimbano ibintu  byerekanwe ntabwo ari ukuri. Ubugizi bwa nabi n'ubukene birasanzwe muri Kibera, nyamara hari benshi bazaharanira ubuzima bwiza nubwo ibintu bimeze nabi.
